OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKenyan school book pulled  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter Prophet Muhammad row 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Kenyan publisher has withdrawn a     
OL,6, school book that included a drawing    
OL,7, depicting Prophet Muhammad following an
OL,8, outcry by Muslim leaders and parents.  
OL,10,FThey complained that it was blasphemous
OL,11,Fto draw the prophet and to ask pupils  
OL,12,Fto colour in the illustration.         
OL,14,FMentor Publishing Company said it      
OL,15,Fregretted the "grave" mistake in the   
OL,16,Fbook on Islamic studies for pupils in  
OL,17,Fthe second year of primary school.     
OL,19,FAbout 11% of Kenyans are Muslims, the  
OL,20,Fsecond largest religious group.        
